    <entry>
      <title>Add Custom Icons in Hexo Blog</title>
      <link href="/2025/04/07/addIcon/"/>
      <url>/2025/04/07/addIcon/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Font-Awesome"><a href="#Font-Awesome" class="headerlink" title="Font Awesome"></a>Font Awesome</h2><ol><li>Font Awesome 图标库<br>Hexo 主题（如 Butterfly、NexT）默认支持 Font Awesome 图标，其图标通过样式前缀 + 名称调用，常见类型包括：</li></ol><table><thead><tr><th>图标类型</th><th>前缀</th><th>示例</th><th>效果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>实心图标</td><td>fas</td><td>fas fa-home</td><td>🏠 家</td></tr><tr><td>常规图标</td><td>far</td><td>far fa-clock</td><td>⏳ 时钟</td></tr><tr><td>细体图标</td><td>fal</td><td>fal fa-book</td><td>📚 书籍</td></tr><tr><td>品牌图标</td><td>fab</td><td>fab fa-github</td><td>GitHub 标志</td></tr></tbody></table><ol start="2"><li>常用图标示例<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">menu:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">首页:</span> <span class="string">/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-home</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">归档:</span> <span class="string">/archives/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">far</span> <span class="string">fa-archive</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">标签:</span> <span class="string">/tags/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-tags</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">关于:</span> <span class="string">/about/</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">far</span> <span class="string">fa-user</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">social:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">GitHub:</span> <span class="string">https://github.com/yourname</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fab</span> <span class="string">fa-github</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">微博:</span> <span class="string">https://weibo.com/yourname</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fab</span> <span class="string">fa-weibo</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">邮箱:</span> <span class="string">mailto:your@example.com</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">fas</span> <span class="string">fa-envelope</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><hr><h2 id="第三方图标库（如阿里-Iconfont）"><a href="#第三方图标库（如阿里-Iconfont）" class="headerlink" title="第三方图标库（如阿里 Iconfont）"></a>第三方图标库（如阿里 Iconfont）</h2><p>若需要国内平台图标（如 B 站、知乎等），可通过以下步骤引入阿里 Iconfont：</p><ol><li><p>操作步骤</p><ol><li>创建项目：<br>在阿里 Iconfont选择图标并加入项目，生成在线链接。</li><li>引入 CSS：<br>将生成的 CSS 链接添加到主题配置文件（如_config.butterfly.yml）：<br>Insert the library’s CSS link into your Hexo theme’s configuration file (e.g., _config.butterfly.yml or _config.next.yml):<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">custom_css:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">//at.alicdn.com/t/c/font_xxx.css</span> <span class="comment"># 替换为你的链接</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol></li><li><p>使用图标：<br>在配置中使用iconfont icon-xxx格式，例如：<br>Modify theme settings (e.g., menu, social links) to include icon classes:</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">social:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="string">B站:</span> <span class="string">https://space.bilibili.com/yourid</span> <span class="string">||</span> <span class="string">iconfont</span> <span class="string">icon-bilibili</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Dynamic Icons in Posts<br>Use HTML&#x2F;Markdown in posts:</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;fas fa-camera-retro&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span></span> Camera  </span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;iconfont icon-zhihu&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span></span> Zhihu Link</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>示例图标</p></li></ol><table><thead><tr><th>图标名称</th><th>代码</th><th>效果</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>B 站</td><td>iconfont icon-bilibili</td><td>B 站标志</td></tr><tr><td>微信</td><td>iconfont icon-weixin</td><td>微信标志</td></tr><tr><td>知乎</td><td>iconfont icon-zhihu</td><td>知乎标志</td></tr></tbody></table><hr><h2 id="图片查找资源"><a href="#图片查找资源" class="headerlink" title="图片查找资源"></a>图片查找资源</h2><ol><li>Font Awesome 官方库：</li></ol><ul><li><a href="https://fontawesome.com/icons?f=brands&s=solid">Solid 图标</a></li><li><a href="https://fontawesome.com/icons?f=brands">Brands 图标</a></li></ul><ol start="2"><li>阿里 Iconfont：<br>搜索关键词（如 “B 站图标”“微信图标”）并生成链接</li></ol><hr><h2 id="注意事项"><a href="#注意事项" class="headerlink" title="注意事项"></a>注意事项</h2><p>样式冲突：确保第三方图标库的 CSS 链接在主题配置中正确引入，避免与 Font Awesome 样式冲突。<br>图标大小：可通过 CSS 调整图标大小和颜色：</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.icon-bilibili</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">font-size</span>: <span class="number">24px</span>;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">color</span>: <span class="number">#00a1d6</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>通过以上方法，你可以在 Hexo 博客中灵活使用各类图标，丰富页面展示效果。</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
